# Documentation

Follow `ai-framework/standards/documentation-rules.md` and `{{DOC_COMMENT_STYLE}}` from PROJECT_PARAMETERS.

- Doxygen for C/C++ when DOC_COMMENT_STYLE=Doxygen
- JSDoc for TypeScript/JavaScript
- Docstrings for Python

Public APIs must be documented. Use project language from PROJECT_PARAMETERS.

Do not add noisy comments that restate obvious code.
